<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hunger-n">hunger <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'hʌŋɡə(r)/    美 /'hʌŋɡər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 饥饿：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>satisfy one's hunger
充饥</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The child was weak from hunger and almost fell.
这孩子因为饥饿而变得虚弱，差点摔倒。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 3</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[常用单数] 渴望：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>hunger for</strong> knowledge / success
渴求知识/渴望成功</p></div></div>